						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged and dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1471, Kīlaka, Bhādrapada, śu. 1,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1548 August 4, Saturday</hi> (not verifiable), in the reign of <hi rend="bold">Sadāśiva-Mahārāya.</hi> It registers a gift made for the merit of the <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> <hi rend="bold">Rāmarāja-Viṭhaladēva-Mahā-arasu, Rāmarājaya-Raṅgarāja</hi> and the donor's (name lost) parents <hi rend="bold">Koṇḍamarasaya</hi> and <hi rend="bold">Narasamma.</hi> Mentions <hi rend="bold">Hiriya-Limga-Bōva.</hi></p>						

